abstract: Andy Sullivan shoots five-under-par 67 to take lead as play is suspended for weather at Abu Dhabi Championship in United Arab Emirates; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Jordan Spieth, Rory McIlroy and other big names slid off the leaderboard at the weather-affected Abu Dhabi Championship in the United Arab Emirates.
